parameters: 3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

General Atu: I thought you would be the first ones to
arrive.

General Atu: I remember the day we defeated the dragon
together. At that time, you were the first ones to charge
through the battlefield.

Clea: I understand that coming here and asking this
question may be pointless, but is there no choice but to
fight?

Clea: If what I know is true, then the dragon is being born
to create the next me.

Clea: I cannot condone Caron, who creates humans like me, a
vengeful person who has lost something precious.

General Atu: On that day, when I saw you defeat the dragon,
I felt as if my prey had been stolen from me.

General Atu: However, I thought we had already put that
behind us. Battle is a clash of beliefs.

General Atu: I, who is not attracted to monsters without
convictions, want to face a worthy opponent... someone who
possesses strong beliefs!

General Atu: If something like a dragon were to be born...
rest assured, I will destroy it with all my heart and soul.

General Atu: Come on! The enemy is here! I will never
approve of Rex, he will definitely become a monster.

General Atu: No more words. Crush my beliefs with that
great sword of yours!
Clea: I wasted time on something I already knew.

Clea: With our beliefs... we will definitely make them
retreat from that place!
バトルの中断による処理
General Atu: So it's you guys next...

Imperial Army Elite: We have hostages here! Quietly tell
us the whereabouts of the prince!

General Atu: Stop with this nonsense, hostages won't work
on these guys.

General Atu: They are the ones who literally put their
lives on the line to accomplish their mission.

General Atu: Don't let your guard down... The two pillars
of the Adventurer's Guild are coming at us with all their
might!

General Atu: As expected, Adventurer's Guild...! As
expected, you two are a formidable pair! To partially
destroy my troops...!

Guild Leader Agonia: I'm sorry, but I will annihilate you
all, including you.

Swift Celis: Guild Leader! Reinforcements are coming!
And--

Swift Celis: The rear is reaching its limit, the operation
is already...

Guild Leader Agonia: Ugh, I'm about to talk about something
important. Please listen carefully, it's about the next
Guild Leader.

Guild Leader Agonia: Shimos, you will be the Guild Leader.
We're in an emergency situation, so we'll skip the approval
of the executives.

Shimos of the Unknown Night: What the hell are you saying?!
The teachings of a woman are to never give up until the end,
right?!

Guild Leader Agonia: That's why... I couldn't dodge the
knife... It's probably poisoned.

Guild Leader Agonia: This is my final order, make sure to
accomplish the request.

Guild Leader Agonia: I will try to hold them back for as
long as possible.
Guild Leader Agonia: All of you, survive!
Guild Leader Agonia: Hurry, Shimos! Storge!

Guild Leader Agonia: Don't let anyone break the wings of
the Adventurer's Guild, Futeira!

Shimos of the Unknown Night: ...Apologize to the old lady
first, you idiot!
Celis of the Swift Wind: C-Clea! Clea and the others!

Storge of Compassion: Let's go, Guild Leader... It's Guild
Leader Agonia's final order!
Celis of the Swift Wind: Clea, I...
Celis of the Swift Wind: I'm sorry...

Imperial Army Elite: What can you do alone?! We'll chase
after them--

Former Guild Leader Agonia: I apologize, I returned it to
someone other than the owner.

Former Guild Leader Agonia: Being freed from the burden of
being a guild leader after such a long time, it feels
surprisingly light to me.

Former Guild Leader Agonia: I have received various
nicknames until now... Meteor, Executioner, Fresh Blood...
Please call me whatever you like.
Agonia of Fresh Blood: ...Well, shall we begin?

General Atu: Have we not killed enough yet...! Agonia,
haven't we killed enough already!?

Agonia of Fresh Blood: There should be no doubt that it is
not strange to kill as many enemies as possible, even if it
means being alone, in order to gain any advantage for our
comrades.

Agonia of Fresh Blood: And Clea and the others are almost
there... That girl still has room to grow, it would be a
waste for her to die here.

Agonia of Fresh Blood: Step aside and return my precious
subordinate to me without fail.

General Atu: I've fought with you many times before... but
I've never felt such a threat until now...!

Agonia of Fresh Blood: It's just a difference in what we
love. I love the organization, the comrades gathered there,
and the clients.
Agonia of Fresh Blood: --That's why! Checkmate, Atu.
Imperial Army Elite: General! Please dodge to the side!
General Atu: I have lost this match...

Agonia, the former guild leader: No... the outcome has not
been decided yet. My proud comrades... will continue the
chess match with you...

Agonia, the former guild leader: That's why... I won't let
you get bored... Hahaha, Atu.

Agonia, the former guild leader: I am... the Adventurer's
Guild... itself...

Agonia, the former guild leader: I am the protector of the
Wings of Freedom... I will not betray, lie, or run away...
Imperial Army Elite: General! Are you safe!?
Imperial Army Elite: Hurry, stop that man!

General Atu: Someone, put a cloak on him. He fought as an
enemy, but he deserves respect as a man.

Imperial Army Elite: General, how will these individuals
be treated?
General Atu: The order is to bring Clea back alive.

General Atu: The other three are familiar faces that I will
kill here. It's better than becoming Caron's toys.

General Atu: I'm sorry, Clea... Please resent me for not
being able to kill you.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Clea: General Atu, please protect us...!

General Atu: Ugh... Don't worry about me! Stop him! Don't
let the dragon get closer to the town!

General Atu: So Caron, you planned to bury us all from the
beginning, even summoning these monsters...

General Atu: Even though I knew it all along, I was just
scared of the monster that resides within Lex...

General Atu: I apologize for involving you in my personal
grudge, but I'll need you to bear with it.

Clea: I will never let the person I was on that day be born
again in this town!

General Atu: Damn it, if I let her escape, it'll be a
disgrace...!

Guild Leader Agonia: A new problem has arisen... but it
seems like an opportunity has presented itself.

Guild Leader Agonia: First, in order to sever the sorrow, I
will have you die.
General Atu: You all, get down!
Guild Leader Agonia: Damn, in this position...!
Simos of the Unknown Night: Hey... lend me a hand...

General Atu: It seems fortunate that we are close in
proximity, but...
Guild Leader Agonia: Why are you protecting me...

Simos of the Unknown Night: I didn't intend to save you or
anything...
Simos of the Unknown Night: Who are you, Agonia?

Guild Leader Agonia: I am the Guild Leader of the
Adventurer's Guild, Futera.

Guild Leader Agonia: I am the very essence of the
Adventurer's Guild, unwavering.

Simos of the Unknown Night: That's why, that's why I saved
you... To protect the Adventurer's Guild, it's a promise I
made with the old hag.

Simos of the Unknown Night: You can protect the
organization, something I can't do. But I am also the very
essence of the Adventurer's Guild, this is my role.

Simos of the Unknown Night: Tch... That old hag, asking for
something troublesome.

Simos of the Unknown Night: Hey, what are you looking at...
It's not something to show off! You damn lizard!
Simos of the Unknown Night: Hah, it's nothing special...!
Simos of the Unknown Night: Hey, Clea! Celis!

Simos of the Unknown Night: No matter what, protect Agonia,
even if it means you die, protect her.

Simos of the Unknown Night: As long as she is the Guild
Leader, protect Agonia and safeguard the future of the
Adventurer's Guild, Futera.
Simos of the Unknown Night: Did you understand?!
Clea: Understood, first, let's focus on healing...!

Simos of the Unknown Night: I've been stabbed in the
stomach... Be careful when killing someone who shoots
strange things at you.

Simos of the Unknown Night: I'll kill the monsters that
keep popping up, you guys go inside and kill the wicked old
hag and the lizard!
Guild Leader Agonia: I leave this to you, Simos.

Simos of the Unknown Night: Hah! Who do you think I am,
Agonia?

Guild Leader Agonia: General Atu, how about a temporary
ceasefire? I believe our interests align in protecting the
empire.

General Atu: Right after I tried to kill you by surprise,
you pull that off!

General Atu: Well, it's fine... It's also my own failure
for not being able to stop Caron.

General Atu: Most likely, the interior is filled with the
Dark Faction and a horde of monsters. First, we need to
eliminate them... Let's storm in!

Swift Celis: Let's go too... We can't let Caron have her
way.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Shimosu of the Unknown Night: 'No one gets through here...
Hurry up!'
